teams.ucmTeam
Class UCMTeam

java.lang.Object
  EDU.gatech.cc.is.abstractrobot.ControlSystemS
      EDU.gatech.cc.is.abstractrobot.ControlSystemSS
          teams.ucmTeam.UCMTeam

public abstract class UCMTeam
extends EDU.gatech.cc.is.abstractrobot.ControlSystemSS

UCMTeam is a Control System that represents a team whose robots are controlled based on predefined behaviours. All team players share a team manager.

UCMTeam is an abstract class. To use it you must extend this class and implement the getTeamManager method.

See Also:
Behaviour, TeamManager

Method Detail

Configure

public void Configure()
Configures the team and the robot. The first time it is invoked it creates and configure the team manager. The team manager is obtained with the getTeamManager(). Then it configures each robot using the default behaviours provided by the team manager.
